[I] The New GNU Portable Threads Library

[T] nPth is a library to provide the GNU Pth API and thus a non-preemptive
[T] threads implementation.
[T]
[T] In contrast to GNU Pth is is based on the system's standard threads
[T] implementation. This allows the use of libraries which are not compatible
[T] to GNU Pth

[U] https://www.gnupg.org/software/npth/

[A] The GNUPG Project
